Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my dad's job, my mom and sisters moved overseas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...so starting this spring, I started living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my first time living alone lasted only a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rikka. I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, already. We start school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I attempted to keep my dark chuunibyou history hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...and start life over again in high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...just like I did last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...Takanashi Rikka here foiled me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I command you to awaken, Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, Wicked Lord Shingan! The time of awakening has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,I wanna fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,盗汗夢が続く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,約束しても、心がどこかで怯えてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,一人じゃないって　信じたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,思い続けてるだけで　幸せなんて言えないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,虚ろな自信　背負っていても　君が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,そして私の勇気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,一つの言葉で君の世界を変えられたら、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,二つの恋が進化する
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,本当だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,巡らせた迷いが見つけた答えはいつでも君に導かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,届ける覚悟が様にならなくても素直に伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,心あるがまま　声がきらめく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kanji,,0,0,0,,With the voice 響き渡るよ
