Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:08.51,TL,,0,0,0,,I wanna fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.48,TL,,0,0,0,,The nightmares continue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:31.05,TL,,0,0,0,,Even with our promise, there's fear in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:37.05,TL,,0,0,0,,I really want to believe that I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:42.65,TL,,0,0,0,,Just thinking can't be called happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:48.86,TL,,0,0,0,,Even though you lack self-confidence, you smile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:52.81,TL,,0,0,0,,So become my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:57.25,TL,,0,0,0,,When one word can change your world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:01.77,TL,,0,0,0,,Both of our loves will evolve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.32,TL,,0,0,0,,That's the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:07.24,TL,,0,0,0,,When confusion surrounded me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:11.14,TL,,0,0,0,,The answer always led to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:15.85,TL,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm never prepared to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.35,TL,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:21.11,TL,,0,0,0,,My voice glistens with the contents of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:26.94,TL,,0,0,0,,With the voice, it echoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka, is sunny side up okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dark side up," please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sunny side up" it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave her too many options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the ribbon for my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Was it them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to prepare it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a busy time! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:14.56,OS,,0,0,0,,Note: {\i1}ahoge{\i0} is literally idiot hair, a slim forelock of hair that sticks straight up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll yank out your {\i1}ahoge{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! It's my "charm point"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This spring, Rikka's mother also had to move out of town for work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...which meant Rikka had to live on her own too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Rikka's baggage being moved out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they finally made their move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Her grandfather accidentally terminated the contract on their apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sabotage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you'll have to live with me until you've settled on a new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency Code: Triple Four activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, Rikka came to live with me temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to be woken up by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See it from my point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.78,OS,,0,0,0,,The Priestess wouldn't be okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied to Touka-san and told her I found Rikka an apartment for her alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've been keeping up this facade for about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimera, I give you my demonic fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting used to these red fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it a little try. They're as good as strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're becoming more and more like the Priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you under her influence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The fluid! The green, squishy matter is attacking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stay perfectly still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wiping at it will only make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to dab at it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:53.03,OS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're heading out, please do take a collapsible umbrella with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say we're dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dating, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you get to romance if it has to be concealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even had a normal girlfriend before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...so having a first girlfriend with chunibyo will be even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Things settled down in a way that isn't much different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Guten morgen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Shinka Nibutani, and I'm in the 11th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it another good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,High school two syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say this one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what you promised yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the hieroglyphs, the hateful magic barrier attack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,triggered by the Freemasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our uninvited guests the unfathomable parallel world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean our discussion about performing the Schrodinger's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,cat experiment using Chimera?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Never! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know. How we're living together at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only thing I spoke to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We should visit the real estate agent again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are referring to my new base, it has already been located.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the demon world of the impossibly Wicked One,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,invisible to mere mortals!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were being serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll yank out your antenna hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you lovebirds are already at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Isshiki. Makoto Isshiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! The guy in the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who sacrificed everything for upperclassman Kumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the crew cut guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Crew Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling me that! That version of me is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at my Rock'n'Roll head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isshiki, what happened to your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go visit the student councilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting it all wrong, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair type changed when it grew back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kumin-senpai! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka-chan and Togashi-kun. Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both 11th graders today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're a 12th grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. And it's such a let-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you'll have to study for university.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh, that isn't what I mean. I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because 12th grade is sooo next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it told me to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know? I want to make everyone laugh just like how Morisummer-chan did
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing older brings many changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Morisummer-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning! What are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, Kumin-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am wearing normal attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"How do you do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you experiencing advanced senility?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, if I might have a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Morisummer-chan, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.79,OS,,0,0,0,,DEKO DEKO MIDDLE MIDDLE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, let's make this another spirited school year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a lot of mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but my second year will be completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will claw my way to the top of this school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}The next speech comes from our new students...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}...represented by Dekomori Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}I am the new student representative, Sanae Dekomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}With the warm days of Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}...the trees become enrobed in fresh, new green livery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that she got better grades than you had last year, Nibutani-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Our student lives also begin anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Deko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe everyone knows that there are white and black worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seeing spirits requires the proper heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love is everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, Nibutani-san has fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We share the same class once again, Light Being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Takanashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have another good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanase-sensei is our home room teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They told to get my hair cut for school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd know? This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are we in the same class again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm in Class 3 next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that relief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You made no attempt to hide your relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Togashi-kun, a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Togashi's friend? I'm Nibutani—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Pot, meet kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only bringing this up because we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Tatenashi-san not to mention our middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,memories at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I pondered all summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I pondered about going to this high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really intend to spend three years of my life in that loser's club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Servant to Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,User of the Mjolnir Hammer, Sanae Dekomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...is hereby reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the deviously devious Fake Morisummer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,would dare stage an attack on me in my temporary guise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You are rotten to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now observe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I spin right left, and left right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposing revolutions shall produce a kink between dimensions and space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And by adding an additional revolution, I shall produce unlimited power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! The Mjolnir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have weak semicircular canals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dekomori will not be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.00,OS,,0,0,0,,Rich Cheese (6 pcs)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're such an energetic First Year...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...as a reward, I will give you the cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,love. So. Much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you're overdoing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One must deal with trouble of one's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Paging a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka Takanashi from Year 2, Class 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please report to the staff room immediately. I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka Takanashi from Year 2, Class 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,please report to the staff room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The school has been overrun by terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing. The school mailed at least three to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They all came back returned to sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be due to the fact that my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,existence had been erased from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When we phone you, it says that number is not in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My existence had been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you exist right now, so perhaps it'll go through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My eye! My eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:02.86,OS,,0,0,0,,Far-East Magical Napping Society - Summer Thereof
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed to buy it, but at this rate, it'll get ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just try to take a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here and sit down with us, Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The incubus lives in that coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even one forged in the darkness such as I dare not approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I once experienced a frightening dream while under its influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What did you dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, the light! The Light Being is paralyzing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that in the form of a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had to choose, where would you want to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What we were talking just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding your base and battle formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For the base, the Wicked King Shingan and the Dark Flame Master demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's magical magnetic field is also the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that idiot here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what she did to my costume for Theatre Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}FAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sleeping inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.49,OS,,0,0,0,,PERMANENT MARKER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to search for a new base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For all that...
