Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz-7\pos(930,648)}Deposit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz-7\pos(317,578)}Gratitude Money
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz-7\pos(1095,669)}Gratitude Money
