Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\frz-7\pos(955,155)}Real Estate Worker Kabu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea where you should set up house alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz2\fs20\pos(568,260)}Real Estate Agent
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz2\fs20\pos(752,284)}Apartments, Units
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz2\fs20\pos(769,219)}Room Searching
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz-1\fs20\pos(1044,324)}No Bicycle Parking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I desire a underground labyrinth. With an ancient castle is also okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposite the convenience store, there's a castle with "British Parliament" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! You definitely can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't realize how expensive rent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I knew it might be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't know much about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be barred from this place once I have transferred to my new base?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't come here when I commute to and from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to go to your room to report activity in the magical realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop by to pick you up for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find you a place nearby so I can visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to stay together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Takanashi's apartment is vacant. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you move, Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Toka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We leave for Italy soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you won't give me your new address or answer your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You are attempting to maintain secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Schwing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dekomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to tail Fake Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I, your loyal servant, will buy you the time you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Masters, please evacuate to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize who you're up against?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Natch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the priestess who, in a previous batle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...once force-fed me a mass of rotten dairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't wish for a worthier opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Your hand! Your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,DUMMY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your intent now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're wrong! This isn't what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Fake Morisummer's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It your fault to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I deeply respect you, Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As my master's sister, I am at your command!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to throw me under the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are such good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare for combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Assume positions and prepare to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Be destroyed, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow up, synapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanishment This World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She easily deflected your Dark Matter Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,L!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,L! O!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,L! O! V!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,L! O! V! E!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a physical attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.00,OS,,0,0,0,,(DEMON GOD GUN) MA SHIN GAN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Schwarz Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrostire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's arrostire?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "oven roasted."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You shacked up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're living together as boyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please control your disgusting imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, disgusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're the one with the dirty mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what? I, Dekomori, am always pure of thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone beet red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For a little kid, you have a really dirty mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Be quiet, you big-boobed freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shacking is sooo shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's really not what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that a full grown boy like yourself had no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,....but to shack up with my little sister with whom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,you are in a romantic relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not in a romantic relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You dissolved your pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dumped whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it! I'm saying we are not "shacking up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are living together...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's mostly because I was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,concerned about leaving Rikka on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been almost a week now, and nothing of the sort is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat it, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contract remains unaltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we're not "living together"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's it! We're roommates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a home share situation. You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that logic will fly by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I will permit that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, you cannot live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find her an apartment. If you have a problem with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...I will take Rikka to Italy with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The magical society! The Cardinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I to be imprisoned in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Italy is home to the occult!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vatican, Sixth Sense, I see dead people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Home to the occult?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuzuha, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you were told I was coming back for the new school term.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told? By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka has been living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so bad about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she doesn't have her own place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of rooms here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:21:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was also concerned about leaving Rikka on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would act as supervisor, it should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.21,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please let her stay here just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and find your own place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, my life alone with Rikka came to an abrupt end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.26,OS,,0,0,0,,TOGASHI MAIL FOR NAKANISHI HERE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and three teenagers began life together in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuta's notebook. I forgot to return it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the-?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone new move in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She never was able to get her apartment back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
